article_id:1106,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Facility Event, A Dash of Disaster, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3739bf0bc2fc11cf39af65298331cb15.png,message:<div>A new facility event, A Dash of Disaster, will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582869600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>This event will pit your group of adventurers against bosses of the flame element. You&rsquo;ll also be able to get an event-related reward facility!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3739bf0bc2fc11cf39af65298331cb15.png"></div><div>Crafty cooks and gourmands seeking decadent dishes gather for the Orichalcum Chef, a culinary contest designed to determine the greatest chef in the world! There&#39;s also a dragon lurking around with a hungry look in its eyes and...is that a sentient vegetable?! With a sm&ouml;rg&aring;sbord of characters as diverse as the dishes they&#39;re serving up, this is one meal you won&#39;t want to miss!</div><div><br></div><div>â– Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582869600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583992799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1582696800,update_time1582253280